# ⚠️ Common Mistakes

### ❌ Lazy loading too small components

```js
const Button = lazy(() => import('./Button'));
```

👉 Overhead > benefit

### ❌ Missing Suspense

```js
const Page = lazy(() => import('./Page')); // crashes ❌
```

✅ Always wrap with `<Suspense />`

